      "polite requests"
    ],
    "audioText": "Excuse me, I received this jacket yesterday, but it has a broken zipper. Could I speak to the manager? I would like to get a replacement, please.",
    "question": "这位顾客遇到了什么问题，她希望怎么解决？",
