      "accommodation"
    ],
    "audioText": "Hello, I'm calling about my reservation. I am staying at your hotel from Friday to Sunday. We are arriving at around eight o'clock in the evening. Is the reception open at that time?",
    "question": "这位旅客打电话的主要目的是什么？",
    "options": [
