    "sourceText": "运动员在训练时应该仔细听从教练的指导，以防受伤。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "Athletes should carefully follow their trainer's instructions during training to prevent injuries.",
      "Athletes should listen carefully to their trainer during training to prevent getting hurt.",
      "During training, athletes should carefully follow their trainer's guidance to prevent injuries."
    ],
    "hint": "使用 should + 副词 carefully，以及动词 prevent 来表达安全建议。",
