        "desc": "一名学生在户外操场上踢足球，阳光明媚",
        "prompt": "student kicking soccer ball on outdoor sports field, bright sunny day, green grass and blue sky",
        "imageSvg": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 400\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\">\n  <!-- White Background -->\n  <rect width=\"400\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n\n  <!-- Outdoor Scene Frame (Sky) -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"40\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" rx=\"30\" fill=\"#4A90D9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n\n  <!-- Grass Field -->\n  <path d=\"M 40 240 Q 200 210 360 240 L 360 330 A 30 30 0 0 1 330 360 L 70 360 A 30 30 0 0 1 40 330 Z\" fill=\"#4CAF50\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- White Field Boundary Line -->\n  <path d=\"M 80 360 Q 180 270 360 290\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n\n  <!-- Shadow under Player and Ball -->\n  <ellipse cx=\"150\" cy=\"310\" rx=\"45\" ry=\"10\" fill=\"#388E3C\" />\n  <ellipse cx=\"270\" cy=\"320\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"5\" fill=\"#388E3C\" />\n\n  <!-- Grass Tufts Details -->\n  <path d=\"M 90 280 L 93 270 L 96 280 M 220 310 L 223 300 L 226 310 M 310 260 L 314 250 L 318 260\" stroke=\"#388E3C\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" fill=\"none\" />\n\n  <!-- Shining Sun -->\n  <circle cx=\"90\" cy=\"90\" r=\"22\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  <path d=\"M 90 55 L 90 65 M 90 115 L 90 125 M 55 90 L 65 90 M 115 90 L 125 90\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n\n  <!-- Cloud -->\n  <path d=\"M 280 110 A 15 15 0 0 1 305 100 A 20 20 0 0 1 335 110 A 15 15 0 0 1 330 125 L 285 125 A 12 12 0 0 1 280 110 Z\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n\n  <!-- STUDENT CHARACTER -->\n\n  <!-- Left Arm (Background) -->\n  <polygon points=\"172,152 200,135 205,142 176,160\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <circle cx=\"205\" cy=\"138\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n  <polygon points=\"172,152 184,145 189,152 176,160\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- Left Leg (Supporting Leg) -->\n  <polygon points=\"140,230 130,280 142,282 152,232\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <!-- Left Shoe -->\n  <path d=\"M 130 280 L 128 294 L 152 294 C 156 294, 156 284, 142 282 Z\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- Torso (Red Sportswear Shirt) -->\n  <polygon points=\"145,150 180,155 170,215 140,210\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- Shorts (White) -->\n  <polygon points=\"140,210 170,215 165,235 135,230\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- Head & Face -->\n  <!-- Hair (Back) -->\n  <path d=\"M 156 128 C 152 135 158 142 162 142 C 160 135 160 130 156 128 Z\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n  <!-- Face Skin -->\n  <circle cx=\"172\" cy=\"132\" r=\"18\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <!-- Cap (Backwards) -->\n  <path d=\"M 156 124 A 18 18 0 0 1 188 124 Z\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <path d=\"M 156 124 L 140 128 L 142 134 L 158 128 Z\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <!-- Face Details -->\n  <circle cx=\"180\" cy=\"130\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n  <path d=\"M 178 140 Q 183 143 185 138\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n\n  <!-- Right Leg (Kicking Leg) -->\n  <polygon points=\"158,222 195,205 230,190 225,180 190,195 154,210\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <!-- Right Shoe -->\n  <path d=\"M 224 196 L 248 180 C 255 175, 260 185, 245 198 L 232 205 Z\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- Right Arm (Foreground) -->\n  <polygon points=\"152,162 122,185 116,177 146,154\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <circle cx=\"118\" cy=\"182\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n  <polygon points=\"152,162 138,172 132,164 146,154\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- Motion Lines (Kicking Effect) -->\n  <path d=\"M 255 170 L 240 180 M 265 180 L 250 190 M 250 155 L 235 165\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n\n  <!-- Soccer Ball -->\n  <circle cx=\"285\" cy=\"145\" r=\"20\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <!-- Soccer Ball Patterns -->\n  <polygon points=\"285,137 293,143 290,152 280,152 277,143\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n  <path d=\"M 285 137 L 285 125 M 293 143 L 302 133 M 290 152 L 297 161 M 280 152 L 273 161 M 277 143 L 268 133\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n</svg>",
