      "do not have to",
      "work duties",
      "jobs",
      "secretary"
    ],
    "sourceText": "秘书每天必须回复很多电子邮件，但她不必自己修电脑。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "The secretary has to reply to many emails every day, but she does not have to fix the computers herself.",
      "A secretary has to answer many emails every day, but she doesn't have to repair the computers herself.",
      "The secretary has to respond to many emails every day, but she does not have to fix the computers by herself."
    ],
    "hint": "用 have to 表示必须做的职责，用 do not have to / doesn't have to 表示不必做的事情。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S03"
  },
