        "desc": "一位演员在舞台上表演戏剧，聚光灯照射，红色幕布背景",
        "prompt": "an actor performing on stage in a drama, spotlight overhead, red curtain background, theater setting",
        "imageSvg": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 400\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\">\n  <rect width=\"400\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Curtains (Background) -->\n  <path d=\"M -10,-10 L 120,-10 C 110,80 80,150 90,200 C 100,250 110,300 90,340 L -10,340 Z\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  <path d=\"M 30,-10 C 40,100 30,200 45,340\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <path d=\"M 70,-10 C 80,100 65,200 70,340\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n\n  <path d=\"M 410,-10 L 280,-10 C 290,80 320,150 310,200 C 300,250 290,300 310,340 L 410,340 Z\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  <path d=\"M 370,-10 C 360,100 370,200 355,340\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <path d=\"M 330,-10 C 320,100 335,200 330,340\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n\n  <!-- Wooden Stage Floor -->\n  <polygon points=\"-10,320 410,320 410,410 -10,410\" fill=\"#A1887F\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n  <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"320\" x2=\"40\" y2=\"400\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n  <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"320\" x2=\"140\" y2=\"400\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n  <line x1=\"240\" y1=\"320\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"400\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n  <line x1=\"320\" y1=\"320\" x2=\"360\" y2=\"400\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n\n  <!-- Spotlight Beam & Pool -->\n  <polygon points=\"120,-10 280,-10 320,350 80,350\" fill=\"#FFF9C4\" opacity=\"0.35\" />\n  <ellipse cx=\"200\" cy=\"350\" rx=\"120\" ry=\"25\" fill=\"#FFE082\" opacity=\"0.5\" />\n  \n  <!-- Spotlight Sparkles & Highlight Lines -->\n  <path d=\"M 140,100 L 142,104 L 147,105 L 142,106 L 140,110 L 138,106 L 133,105 L 138,104 Z\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" />\n  <path d=\"M 260,120 L 262,124 L 267,125 L 262,126 L 260,130 L 258,126 L 253,125 L 258,124 Z\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" />\n  <line x1=\"150\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"110\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\" />\n  <line x1=\"250\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\" />\n\n  <!-- Valance (Top Curtain) -->\n  <path d=\"M -10,-10 L 410,-10 L 410,50 Q 300,90 200,50 Q 100,90 -10,50 Z\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n  <!-- Actor Character -->\n  <g id=\"actor\">\n    <!-- Cape (Behind Actor) -->\n    <path d=\"M 175,200 C 135,210 115,260 125,315 C 145,325 170,305 175,275 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n    <path d=\"M 225,200 C 265,210 285,260 275,315 C 255,325 230,305 225,275 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n\n    <!-- Legs & Boots -->\n    <line x1=\"180\" y1=\"275\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"340\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"12\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n    <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"275\" x2=\"230\" y2=\"340\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"12\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n    <path d=\"M 155,342 L 175,342 L 175,350 L 150,350 Z\" fill=\"#8D6E63\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n    <path d=\"M 225,342 L 245,342 L 250,350 L 225,350 Z\" fill=\"#8D6E63\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n\n    <!-- Tunic & Belt -->\n    <path d=\"M 165,200 L 235,200 Q 245,240 235,275 L 165,275 Q 155,240 165,200 Z\" fill=\"#4A90D9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n    <path d=\"M 164,255 L 236,255 L 235,267 L 165,267 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n    <rect x=\"194\" y=\"252\" width=\"12\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n\n    <!-- Left Arm (Gesturing Up) -->\n    <path d=\"M 153,198 L 125,150 L 137,143 L 165,191 Z\" fill=\"#4A90D9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n    <path d=\"M 125,147 L 112,135 C 108,130 115,125 120,132 L 133,141 Z\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n    <circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"205\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#4A90D9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n    <!-- Right Arm (Holding Mask) -->\n    <path d=\"M 245,205 L 275,230 L 270,240 L 240,215 Z\" fill=\"#4A90D9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n    <circle cx=\"275\" cy=\"235\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n    <circle cx=\"240\" cy=\"205\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#4A90D9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n    <!-- Theatrical Mask on Stick -->\n    <line x1=\"275\" y1=\"235\" x2=\"287\" y2=\"180\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n    <path d=\"M 270,150 C 270,130 305,130 305,150 C 305,175 290,190 287,190 C 285,190 270,175 270,150 Z\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n    <circle cx=\"280\" cy=\"152\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n    <circle cx=\"295\" cy=\"152\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n    <path d=\"M 282,170 Q 287,163 293,170\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n\n    <!-- Neck & Head -->\n    <path d=\"M 192,175 L 208,175 L 205,200 L 195,200 Z\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n    <circle cx=\"200\" cy=\"155\" r=\"24\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" />\n\n    <!-- Hair -->\n    <circle cx=\"178\" cy=\"150\" r=\"9\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n    <circle cx=\"222\" cy=\"150\" r=\"9\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n    <circle cx=\"180\" cy=\"162\" r=\"9\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n    <circle cx=\"220\" cy=\"162\" r=\"9\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n    <path d=\"M 178,145 Q 200,133 222,145\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n\n    <!-- Crown -->\n    <polygon points=\"188,140 192,123 200,133 208,123 212,140\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n\n    <!-- Face Details -->\n    <path d=\"M 187,156 Q 192,160 195,156\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n    <path d=\"M 205,156 Q 208,160 213,156\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" />\n    <ellipse cx=\"200\" cy=\"168\" rx=\"5\" ry=\"8\" fill=\"#333333\" />\n    <circle cx=\"182\" cy=\"164\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#FF8A80\" opacity=\"0.6\" />\n    <circle cx=\"218\" cy=\"164\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#FF8A80\" opacity=\"0.6\" />\n  </g>\n\n  <!-- Footlights (Front of Stage) -->\n  <path d=\"M 65,400 L 95,400 L 90,385 L 70,385 Z\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n  <path d=\"M 70,385 A 10,10 0 0 1 90,385 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n\n  <path d=\"M 185,400 L 215,400 L 210,385 L 190,385 Z\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n  <path d=\"M 190,385 A 10,10 0 0 1 210,385 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n\n  <path d=\"M 305,400 L 335,400 L 330,385 L 310,385 Z\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n  <path d=\"M 310,385 A 10,10 0 0 1 330,385 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n</svg>",
