      {
        "desc": "一个人在电影院感到害怕，缩在座位上，手遮住眼睛",
        "prompt": "person in dark cinema seat, covering eyes with hands, scared expression, red seats, dark background with faint screen glow",
        "imageSvg": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 400\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\">\n  <rect width=\"400\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Floor Shadow -->\n  <ellipse cx=\"200\" cy=\"345\" rx=\"120\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"#E0E0E0\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Cinema Seat Backrest -->\n  <rect x=\"110\" y=\"100\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" rx=\"25\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  <rect x=\"125\" y=\"115\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" rx=\"15\" fill=\"#C62828\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Seat Cushion -->\n  <rect x=\"95\" y=\"270\" width=\"210\" height=\"45\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Armrests -->\n  <rect x=\"75\" y=\"240\" width=\"40\" height=\"18\" rx=\"5\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  <rect x=\"285\" y=\"240\" width=\"40\" height=\"18\" rx=\"5\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Character Hood Back -->\n  <circle cx=\"200\" cy=\"200\" r=\"52\" fill=\"#2E7D32\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Character Torso -->\n  <path d=\"M 125 285 C 125 240, 160 230, 200 230 C 240 230, 275 240, 275 285 Z\" fill=\"#4CAF50\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Hoodie Rim Details & Drawstrings -->\n  <path d=\"M 155 230 Q 200 215 245 230\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n  <path d=\"M 188 230 Q 183 250 190 260 M 212 230 Q 217 250 210 260\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Face -->\n  <circle cx=\"200\" cy=\"205\" r=\"42\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Hair -->\n  <path d=\"M 158 195 C 158 170, 242 170, 242 195 C 220 185, 210 185, 200 195 C 190 185, 180 185, 158 195 Z\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Scared Eyes (Behind Fingers) -->\n  <ellipse cx=\"178\" cy=\"198\" rx=\"9\" ry=\"11\" fill=\