      "passive voice",
      "recycling",
      "pollution",
      "rubbish"
    ],
    "audioText": "In our city, rubbish is collected every Monday morning. Plastic bottles and paper are separated and recycled. Glass is also collected and sent to the factory. The air near the factory is sometimes polluted by smoke, but new machines are used to reduce the pollution.",
    "question": "根据录音内容，以下哪项描述是正确的？",
    "options": [
      "垃圾每周二早上被收集，塑料瓶和玻璃一起回收。",
      "工厂附近的空气没有任何污染，新机器完全消除了烟雾。",
      "垃圾每周一早上被收集，塑料瓶和纸张被分开回收。"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 2,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U09-S03"
  },
