      "stress",
      "giving reasons"
    ],
    "sourceText": "我压力很大，因为作业太多了。一个解决方法是更好地管理我的时间。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "I have a lot of stress because of too much homework. One solution is to manage my time better.",
