      "going to",
      "travel plans",
      "destination",
      "climate"
    ],
    "audioText": "We are going to travel to the coast next summer. The climate there is warm and sunny, so it is a perfect option for us. We are going to arrange everything according to the season.",
    "question": "他们打算去哪里旅行，原因是什么？",
    "options": [
      "他们打算去海岸旅行，因为那里气候温暖晴朗。",
      "他们打算去另一个大陆旅行，因为那里有宫殿和湖泊。",
      "他们打算去山谷旅行，因为那里有古老的城堡。"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 0,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U04-S01"
  },
