    "audioText": "Yesterday, I was walking down the stairs when I suddenly slipped and fell. I hit my arm on the ground very hard. Fortunately, it was not broken, but it was very painful. I fell because the stairs were wet.",
    "question": "根据听力内容，这个人的手臂怎么了？",
    "options": [
