      "environment",
      "flood",
      "suggestion"
    ],
    "audioText": "Floods are becoming more serious every year. Firstly, if we plant more trees, we will reduce the risk of floods. Secondly, if people are more careful with water, we will save a lot of clean water. Finally, if we all work together, we will achieve our goal and solve this problem.",
