        "desc": "一群人在巨大湖边扎营，地面有大坑",
        "prompt": "people camping in tents beside a very large blue lake outdoors at night, a big deep hole visible in the ground nearby, green trees, dark sky with stars",
        "imageSvg": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 400\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\">\n  <!-- White Background -->\n  <rect width=\"400\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n  \n  <defs>\n    <clipPath id=\"camp-frame\">\n      <rect x=\"30\" y=\"30\" width=\"340\" height=\"340\" rx=\"40\" />\n    </clipPath>\n  </defs>\n  \n  <!-- Camp Scene Group clipped to the rounded rect -->\n  <g clip-path=\"url(#camp-frame)\">\n    <!-- Sky Background (same color as water: #4A90D9) -->\n    <rect x=\"20\" y=\"20\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" fill=\"#4A90D9\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Stars -->\n    <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"80\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"120\" cy=\"65\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"180\" cy=\"90\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"70\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"330\" cy=\"95\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Moon -->\n    <path d=\"M 285 55 A 18 18 0 0 1 310 80 A 20 20 0 0 0 285 55 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Distant Forest/Trees line (separating Sky and Lake) -->\n    <path d=\"M 20 145 L 45 110 L 70 145 L 90 115 L 115 145 L 130 120 L 155 145 L 190 145 L 210 110 L 235 145 L 250 125 L 270 145 L 295 115 L 320 145 L 340 120 L 365 145 L 380 145 L 380 160 L 20 160 Z\" fill=\"#4CAF50\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Wave lines on the lake -->\n    <path d=\"M 60 165 L 100 165 M 140 185 L 195 185 M 230 160 L 270 160 M 295 180 L 335 180\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Foreground Land (Grassy bank) -->\n    <path d=\"M 20 210 Q 120 190 200 215 T 380 200 L 380 380 L 20 380 Z\" fill=\"#4CAF50\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Tent 1 (Left) -->\n    <polygon points=\"50,235 85,185 120,235\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n    <!-- Tent 1 Opening -->\n    <polygon points=\"70,235 85,205 100,235\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n    <polygon points=\"70,235 85,205 75,235\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Tent 2 (Right) -->\n    <polygon points=\"215,225 245,180 275,225\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n    <!-- Tent 2 Opening -->\n    <polygon points=\"233,225 245,200 257,225\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Campfire Logs -->\n    <line x1=\"150\" y1=\"268\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"258\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    <line x1=\"190\" y1=\"268\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"258\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    <!-- Fire Flame -->\n    <path d=\"M 170 262 Q 152 232 170 207 Q 188 237 170 262 Z\" fill=\"#FFC107\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n    <path d=\"M 170 262 Q 160 242 170 227 Q 180 242 170 262 Z\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"none\"/>\n    <!-- Fire Sparks -->\n    <circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"192\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#FFC107\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"178\" cy=\"182\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#FFC107\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Camper 1 (Left) -->\n    <rect x=\"105\" y=\"260\" width=\"30\" height=\"12\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n    <rect x=\"110\" y=\"235\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" rx=\"5\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"120\" cy=\"222\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\"/>\n    <path d=\"M 128 244 L 143 248\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Camper 2 (Right) -->\n    <rect x=\"195\" y=\"238\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" rx=\"5\" fill=\"#E53935\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"205\" cy=\"225\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\"/>\n    <path d=\"M 197 246 L 182 250\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Foreground Big Deep Hole: Dirt Piles -->\n    <path d=\"M 140 340 Q 165 315 190 340 Z\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\"/>\n    <path d=\"M 305 330 Q 325 305 345 330 Z\" fill=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\"/>\n    \n    <!-- The Hole itself -->\n    <ellipse cx=\"245\" cy=\"330\" rx=\"70\" ry=\"25\" fill=\"#333333\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n    \n    <!-- Shovel in left dirt pile -->\n    <g>\n      <line x1=\"150\" y1=\"295\" x2=\"162\" y2=\"328\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <line x1=\"145\" y1=\"297\" x2=\"155\" y2=\"293\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <polygon points=\"158,324 168,321 164,334\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n    </g>\n    \n    <!-- Ladder sticking out of the hole -->\n    <g>\n      <!-- Rails -->\n      <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"285\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"345\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"5.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <line x1=\"238\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"258\" y2=\"340\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"5.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <!-- Wooden inner rails -->\n      <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"285\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"345\" stroke=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <line x1=\"238\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"258\" y2=\"340\" stroke=\"#FFD1A9\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <!-- Rungs -->\n      <line x1=\"223\" y1=\"298\" x2=\"241\" y2=\"292\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <line x1=\"229\" y1=\"316\" x2=\"247\" y2=\"310\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <line x1=\"235\" y1=\"334\" x2=\"253\" y2=\"328\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    </g>\n    \n    <!-- Grass Tufts -->\n    <path d=\"M 125 315 L 128 307 L 132 315\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    <path d=\"M 285 295 L 288 288 L 292 295\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    <path d=\"M 335 350 L 338 342 L 342 350\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    <path d=\"M 80 340 L 83 332 L 87 340\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  </g>\n  \n  <!-- Outer border of the frame -->\n  <rect x=\"30\" y=\"30\" width=\"340\" height=\"340\" rx=\"40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#333333\" stroke-width=\"8\"/>\n</svg>",
        "imageUrl": "/api/images/pair_1782569237717-A2-U10-S01-004-opt2.jpg?v=1783893747401"
