    "sourceText": "我去年去露营了，那是一次非常特别的经历。我们在一个巨大的森林里搭帐篷，我几乎在树下睡着了。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "I went camping last year, and it was a very special experience. We set up our tents in an enormous forest, and I nearly fell asleep under a tree.",
